<h2>Ahen's News</h2>

<div class="news-section">
{% for post in collections.posts %}
  <div class="news-item">
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    <div class="post-meta">Sector: {{ post.data.sector }} | Rating: {{ post.data.rating }} | Date: {{ post.date.toDateString() }}{% if post.data.source %} | Source: {{ post.data.source | safe }}{% endif %}</div>
  </div>
{% endfor %}
</div>

<hr>

<h3>Create a New Post</h3>
<p>To create a new post, add a new Markdown file to the <code>/posts</code> directory.</p>
<p>You can also use the <a href="/editor.html">simple editor</a>.</p>